  <compounddef id="classaetherion_1_1VaporMovementBlockedException" kind="class" language="C++" prot="public">
    <compoundname>aetherion::VaporMovementBlockedException</compoundname>
    <basecompoundref refid="classaetherion_1_1MovementException" prot="public" virt="non-virtual">aetherion::MovementException</basecompoundref>
    <includes refid="PhysicsExceptions_8hpp" local="no">PhysicsExceptions.hpp</includes>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Exception thrown when vapor upward movement is blocked and should diffuse sideways. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Thrown by <computeroutput>moveVaporUp</computeroutput> when upward movement cannot proceed (e.g. moving obstruction or no suitable vapor above to merge). The orchestrator can catch this and call <computeroutput>moveVaporSideways</computeroutput> to attempt lateral diffusion. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
